---
title: Bangers 'n' Mash Pie with Cabbage and Pancetta
description: What’s better than sausage and mash? You guessed it, sausage and mash pie! Made with earthy veggies, sausage and salty pancetta lardons and baked until golden on top, this wholesome dish is guaranteed to please everyone around the dinner table.
